The paper also discusses sparsity thresholds, which is a topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and signal processing (cs.SP). Additionally, the paper uses coherence parameters, which is a topic in numerical analysis (cs.NA) and the paper's approach of splitting the dictionary can be seen as a form of dictionary learning, which is a topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and signal processing (cs.SP).
